snippet.title: Mini Matches - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Mini Matches is a 1 to 4 player online and local-multiplayer party game.

Race, shoot, golf, jump, and compete with your friends across a series of frenetic rounds. Level up to unlock new characters and power up your abilities in the extensive upgrade tree.

Available now on Steam
https://itsanecdotal.com/minimatches/

Music by Monkey Warhol - Boots & Pants (Instrumental Mix)
